    <description>Screen flow launched from Active Gov Licensee Accounts that confirms parent account and contact; confirms customer type; create close won oppty. JH 6/26/23- This version removes licensee opp owner getting automatically set to Neydi Contreras and account getting updated to customer and onboarding account status. JH 8/16/23- stamps the original close date 1 day after opp is created instead of same day
1.10.24 - DJ - Updated default Close Date to be TODAY() + 30 from request on this Asana Ticket: [Government 2024-01-02 15:22:20] Gov Deals Not Showing Automatic 30 Day Close Date</description>
    <environments>Default</environments>
    <formulas>
        <name>NextDayDate</name>
        <dataType>Date</dataType>
        <expression>TODAY()+30</expression>
    </formulas>
    <formulas>
        <name>OpportunityNameFormula</name>
        <dataType>String</dataType>
        <expression>{!Get_Starting_Account.Name}&amp;&quot; - &quot;&amp;&quot;Licensee of &quot;&amp;{!RelatedPayerAccount.recordName}</expression>
    </formulas>
    <formulas>
        <name>OriginalCloseDateFormula</name>
        <dataType>Date</dataType>
        <expression>IF(ISBLANK({!Get_Starting_Account.Original_Close_Date__c}),TODAY(),{!Get_Starting_Account.Original_Close_Date__c})</expression>
    </formulas>
